---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Tai from "../../assets/officerImgs/TaisPhoto.png";
---

<div
  class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto sm:max-w-xl md:max-w-full lg:max-w-screen-xl md:px-24 lg:px-8 lg:py-20"
>
  <div class="w-4/5 mx-auto text-center mb-10 md:mx-auto md:mb-12">
    <h2 class="tracking-tight text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl">
      Celebrating Our Trailblazers: Notable Alumni
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="w-5/6 mx-auto text-center mb-10 md:mx-auto md:mb-12">
    <p class="tracking-tight text-m md:text-l lg:text-xl">
      Our alumni are the foundation of Oregon State NSBE, paving the way with
      their achievements and leadership. This page honors those who have made
      significant contributions by highlighting where they are at now and how
      OSU NSBE has impacted them. Discover where our most notable alumni have
      advanced in their careers.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid px-8 gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
    <div>
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden transition duration-300 transform rounded shadow-lg lg:hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl"
      >
        <Image
          src={Tai}
          alt="Tai"
          class="object-cover w-full h-56 md:h-64 xl:h-80"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center px-5 py-4 text-center transition-opacity duration-300 bg-black bg-opacity-75 opacity-0 hover:opacity-100"
        >
          <p class="mb-1 text-lg font-bold text-gray-100">Tai-Ren√©e King</p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs text-gray-100">President</p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs text-gray-100">
            Natural Resources with Minor in Humanitarian Engineering
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs tracking-wide text-gray-400">
            I love roller skating, video games, and learning new things.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
